{"tid":1765630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際戰線: 媒體輸出 - Hong Kong Free Press","createTime":"2019-12-02T04:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T09:25:48.000Z","uid":285924,"like":84,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"9b8b6ebcc50c423758bbab80e3192193ca5eb277","tid":1765630,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"發現Hong Kong Free Press (香港自由新聞) 呢間媒體冇乜人講，<br />\nHKFP係一間本地英文<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">金</span></span>媒，<br />\n其實佢地嘅記者係前線同手足齊上齊落左好耐，為香港報導事實真相，<br />\n好多在港嘅外籍人士都係靠睇佢地嘅報導同直播先知發生緊咩事，好多外國人亦都係透過HKFP睇到第一手香港新聞。<br />\n<br />\n聽個名都知呢間良心媒體同我地一樣咁熱愛自由，<br />\n有睇開佢嘅朋友形容為英文版立場。<br />\n有睇開直播嘅朋友應該可以認得佢地嘅總編輯 Tom Grundy (中間)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HSbsDZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHSbsDZH.jpg&h=bae275af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經常親自落場直播，體會同其他前線記者一齊食tg同警棍。<br />\n甚至曾經因為報道中共事實，六四同人權議題收過恐嚇信:<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171005/20173180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171005%2F20173180&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0VT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=cc6f23f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171005%2F20173180&h=f0a7608c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171005/20173180</a><br />\n<br />\n如果識得有外國朋友想了解運動，歡迎share比佢地。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣了解HKFP嘅朋友 (或者想學英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ，可以上佢地網頁望下。或者係fb比個Like:<br />\n<br />\nPage: <a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0VT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=d9eabd6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/</a><br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkongfp%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0VT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=d5055513\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkongfp/</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地係非牟利媒體，小小希望有心嘅朋友亦都可以經濟上支持佢地，香港人唔會忘記HKFP。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/support-hkfp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2Fsupport-hkfp%2F&d=uyenQRwN%2F2p2tRNf%2Bb8L0VT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=5f1ae3dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/support-hkfp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n解散警隊，刻不容緩。"},{"pid":"477d6e0b272d135af19d60d1f27dbe80cabf4463","tid":1765630,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"推！好多鬼佬都係靠紅色資本SCMP接觸相關資訊<br />\n要大力推廣HKFP俾國際讀者"},{"pid":"83e0cc04cf007ceb9d7f497ce2500381c13f388d","tid":1765630,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"P牌自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1/10"},{"pid":"faaafd5887e4e022bf0927274813a71db3e288a9","tid":1765630,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"477d6e0b272d135af19d60d1f27dbe80cabf4463","tid":1765630,"uid":101392,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:21.000Z","msg":"推！好多鬼佬都係靠紅色資本SCMP接觸相關資訊<br />\n要大力推廣HKFP俾國際讀者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a06d872dbbf1250a615c10f68828c349ed3990db","tid":1765630,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"97c22f3beb88eb8626c229509234b5c5acc431fe","tid":1765630,"uid":285924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c